## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible motivations for firms competing for the Malcolm Baldrige Award. Additionally, the information is subject to the limitations of the sources used, which may not provide a comprehensive view of all industry perspectives. Further research, including interviews with industry experts and award recipients, could provide deeper insights into the motivations and benefits associated with the award.